===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bókè
===Etymology===
Sound borrowing from English "[[blog]]"; from [[博]] ("abundant," "plentiful," "wide," "broad," "rich") + [[客]] ("guest," "visitor"). The term was coined in 2002 by Beijing technology writer Fang Xingdong.

